{"tid":1974130,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，English studies 定 linguistics好？","createTime":"2020-04-15T15:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T02:57:27.000Z","uid":287373,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb9fa3a28fe85da72844daed03d06b4d930c298","tid":1974130,"uid":287373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"講返少少背景，小弟non-jupas收到兩個offers，English studies同linguists. <br />\n如果揀English， 就打算考pdge中小學，或者睇下自身能力再進修master+PhD，希望做到lecturer.<br />\n如果讀Linguistics，個方向就大概一樣，但就撇除左中小學老師呢個選擇，希望進修言語治療。<br />\n我見過上面兩個theme都有人成功進修言語治療。<br />\n<br />\n問題來了，我讀過phonetics phonology方面，雖然香港出世，但真係分唔到廣東話pang, pan 朋貧呢d，但反而英文果邊就好熟。咁樣係咪代表言語治療已經冇可能？<br />\n同埋linguistics我唔鍾意佢個概念好虛e.g. Theme, rheme, genre，有少少難明，但我覺得functional grammar好有趣...<br />\n有冇師兄有過類似疑問啟蒙下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3679d5b3056fe3180a115a74de1f88bd300714fb","tid":1974130,"uid":287373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"唔記得講邊間，兩科都係CityU，聽講city linguistics好似唔錯？再加上我知有個prof當初都係讀呢科，去埋澳洲進修完返來教書"},{"pid":"61b2120c1c38486d4bd9d47b1016801b3b4734e9","tid":1974130,"uid":274123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci